title: GameHouse Games - Little Shop  Memories - New Hidden Object - We
description:
Little Shop Memories v1.0.0.52


Take a trip down Memory Lane as you prepare for your move to paradise. 

Discover photos, trinkets and other keepsakes that trigger memories 

from your road to becoming a successful Little Shop entrepreneur. 

Explore twelve environments, spanning five decades, all starting with 

that first lemonade stand in the 1960's. Play four types of Bonus 

Rounds to progress the story and unlock new chapters from your past.

Thanx to TAC-CM
